 Li Mi:\nThe French Foreign Office has asked the French High Commissioner in Saigon \"to refuse formally any visa for Indochina to General Li Mi, Commander of the Chinese Nationalist units which are operating in upper Burma.\"\n\nComment: Burma had asked France to take this step in order to prevent Li Mi's return to that country from Formosa. Present indications are that he will not return to Burma, and there is no evidence that he intends to seek entry into Indochina", "token_count": 90, "token_end_0based": 89, "token_start_0based": 0, "token_text": "4 france would refuse transit of indochina to general li mi the french foreign office has asked the french high commissioner in saigon to refuse formally any visa for indochina to general li mi commander of the chinese nationalist units which are operating in upper burma comment burma had asked france to take this step in order to prevent li mi's return to that country from formosa present indications are that he will not return to burma and there is no evidence that he intends to seek entry into indochina", "unred_source_page": 6}
